replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:36:39.000Z","msg":"有冇專家用簡單中文conclude即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"即係支那懶醒搵一個做法去跳過 美國佬要控制既要求，事實上而加個交易完左都係大陸公司控制。所以美帝係醒既就應該ban鳩佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:55:46.000Z","msg":"只係technically 美國投資者有53%收益權，非直接控制。so its a trash number"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:57:51.000Z","msg":"呢個transactional structure一定係班懶醒既ibanker + lawyer 以為自己好叻叻兩邊都殺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實有小小腦都會ban鳩佢"},{"pid":"e866540035966c361311e8aca72c921beaf4abc8","tid":2212454,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T00:03:50.000Z","msg":"胡總又炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/huxijin_gt/status/1308041396209688578?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhuxijin_gt%2Fstatus%2F1308041396209688578%3Fs%3D21&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEQzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=6e27105d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhuxijin_gt%2Fstatus%2F1308041396209688578%3Fs%3D21&h=fafdc6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/huxijin_gt/status/1308041396209688578?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"a66dbd23c74859a4c96ad30585b088d7cb878561","tid":2212454,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c68be3c304f8f46f962d6661dfe1b06a3ea944c","tid":2212454,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb7ec95b201a136c9b71d9b606a429576ef42aa","tid":2212454,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae8058404fe0b26d28864aa9d3ede9683b282754","tid":2212454,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:54:28.000Z","msg":"即係支那懶醒搵一個做法去跳過 美國佬要控制既要求，事實上而加個交易完左都係大陸公司控制。所以美帝係醒既就應該ban鳩佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:55:46.000Z","msg":"只係technically 美國投資者有53%收益權，非直接控制。so its a trash number"},"citedB